cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper presents a transformer-based network for MRI radiology report classification, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), which are all relevant to the paper's methodology and application.
